"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"This [public art work speaking to the growing refugee crisis around the worl](https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/goodchance/the-walk-the-most-ambitious-public-artwork-of-our-time)d is really great. I backed it earlier this week when I saw my friend Sunny back it.\\n\\n> From July to November 2021, a giant puppet of a 9-year-old Syrian refugee girl called ‘Little Amal’ will walk from the Syria-Turkey border, across Europe to the UK, travelling 8,000km to focus awareness on the refugee crisis. [***The Walk***](https://www.walkwithamal.org/) is an international arts festival meets endurance event – the length and sheer size of the challenge is capturing imaginations even before our heroine’s first step.\\n\\nI’ve posted the video into this blog post but if you are reading on Mirror or via email, [click here and watch it](https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/goodchance/the-walk-the-most-ambitious-public-artwork-of-our-time#).\\n\",\"timestamp\":1620986877,\"title\":\"Funding Friday: The Walk\",\"publication\":\"avc\"},\"digest\":\"SbeEbNxzfijVjr0gs1P1I_ArMmj6WoVpy6ZARQrbJ88\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB8332710AB60A1B2e8FE6D775d83524C9E0cE136\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"LTl3aLSRol2QUVUD6CZDmgOh-_8_repOG-vj-b00m1o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Q21DlwnMAzKTxzvSjREQR-eWtchCVIOEf9pQ8-_jbbs\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"nKKB5OF1nniHoJDeC1QjLObPsqyzvia5IhKDWv5xhDQDnSqyhSY9Zkn4gIZD0aceLCPKiJ78xcXtnqTp_MY_ng\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa36ed4a1f484cc32e85a01be266ff07df93d7d551959ab6f44e5cb7aca49bba22841e81a419ff9150996b75ecf4a0a87eda7e1e79898e4f8e48a13744383f7451b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on avc.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"LTl3aLSRol2QUVUD6CZDmgOh-_8_repOG-vj-b00m1o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Q21DlwnMAz